### Criar Tarefa
POST http://localhost:3333/tasks HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "title": "Estudar php",
    "description": "Description"
}

### Listar as tarefas
GET http://localhost:3333/tasks HTTP/1.1

### Ver Tarefa Especifica
GET http://localhost:3333/tasks/f06cb8e9-bf30-43fa-8e91-1817dfb67ef0 HTTP/1.1

### Atualizar Tarefa pelo id
PUT http://localhost:3333/tasks/f06cb8e9-bf30-43fa-8e91-1817dfb67ef0 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "title": "Estudar node up",
    "description": "descr"
}

### Deleta uma Tarefa pelo id
DELETE  http://localhost:3333/tasks/f06cb8e9-bf30-43fa-8e91-1817dfb67ef0 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Completa Tarefa pelo id
PATCH  http://localhost:3333/tasks/f06cb8e9-bf30-43fa-8e91-1817dfb67ef0 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json